player default abilities:
1. Charge move - player charges shot for 1 1/2 seconds.
2. Dash - player can dash at any of the eight directions to avoid any damage.
3. Overload - when the battery is fully charged it can overload and destroy the player, but dispersing a lot of damage.

chip abilities:
1. faster recharge
2. Higher jump
3. Hover
4. Faster weapon
5. Elemental damage
        a. Fire
        b. Earth
        c. Ice
        d. Electric
6. More battery
7. battery drain
